extendedInfo.description: Fancy JigSaw is a classic puzzle game. Drag the Little Princess pieces to the right place to re-establish the full picture. Don't sweat it if you are unable to solve the puzzle easily. You can use the peek button to preview the original image.There are 100 levels in this game. The further you advance, the more challenging the puzzle becomes. This app also allows you to save the Little Princess images to your SD .These little lolita fairies(elves)  are beauty and funny, melancholy and jolly, but always very nice, with deep beautiful eyes, open smile and enigmatic glance. We corrected a SPECIAL collection of sweet, cute, lolita, and erotic pictures of fairies.Let's enjoy their life and their world!!Cool Features Include:- More than 100 pictures of Little Princess- Multiple difficulty levels (from 3*3 to the most difficult 7*7).- Save to phone album function.- Images gallery and difficulty selection.Fancy JigSaw is suitable for a wide range of audiences, Many different modes and pictures in the game will keep you excited and entertained for a long time.Keywords:puzzle,puzzles,Jigsaw,games,brainfun,funny,Little Princess,entertainment,wallpapers,lolita fairies
